                "description": "D\u1ECDn ph\xF2ng h\xE0ng ng\xE0y t\u1EEB 9h-11h s\xE1ng. Bao g\u1ED3m: thay ga g\u1ED1i, d\u1ECDn d\u1EB9p ph\xF2ng, v\u1EC7 sinh ph\xF2ng t\u1EAFm, thay kh\u0103n t\u1EAFm, b\u1ED5 sung \u0111\u1ED3 v\u1EC7 sinh c\xE1 nh\xE2n. D\u1ECBch v\u1EE5 mi\u1EC5n ph\xED cho kh\xE1ch l\u01B0u tr\xFA.",
